{"tid":2205313,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"關於App testing，小弟想請教下各位","createTime":"2020-09-16T17:20:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-03T10:48:58.000Z","uid":124400,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"caa24f39f53ab2f71e0d27d70488fd5d6605e4b1","tid":2205313,"uid":124400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T17:20:02.000Z","msg":"係咁嘅，小弟幾個月前新手用React native寫左個App，寫完擺左上App store，個App一開始無咩人理，但係一直都有keep住update，呢幾日突然多左好多人，一日有40-50人安裝左右，咁就想繼續做好D<br />\n<br />\n由於小弟一直都係自學，沒咩實際經驗，平時update / fix bug 都係拎住部電話自己做QA，但問題係有時搞搞下會唔小心郁到d major function又不自知，我又無可能逐個功能試，有幾次到 release 左先都無發現有問題，唔係 user 同返我講我都唔知 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想請教下師兄們業界一般係點確保個 App 係 release 前無錯誤，上網睇過有 Jest 之類嘅 Library，但係關於點樣用嚟 test d react hook 嘅文章又好少，有沒bro幫下我? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbc6b50c3c272ba9afb601b01450b92abb58b55e","tid":2205313,"uid":124400,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T17:31:03.000Z","msg":"Jest 我琴晚試過，用嚟 test pure function 之類都ok嘅，但係我見人可以成個 component 例如 App.js 咁去 test。我自己試過下，彈左一大堆 error出嚟，上網睇話如果有component 入面如果有 import 其他 module 就要同佢地做 mocking <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係咁多 module 點逐個做 mocking<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有沒師兄俾方向我"},{"pid":"e47ecc5658bf545cd9b86a6df1a007888944271f","tid":2205313,"uid":106870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T17:32:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05619b826d60ad18721194462cbf323c48f00593","tid":2205313,"uid":124400,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e47ecc5658bf545cd9b86a6df1a007888944271f","tid":2205313,"uid":106870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T17:32:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T17:35:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56b65308d84199cb14cf25ba2c35bfe7a8fea0b2","tid":2205313,"uid":124400,"like":0,"dislike":25,"score":-25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T17:45:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zxb6fKE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZxb6fKE.gif&h=cc52ddd3&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g2Gqwh0.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg2Gqwh0.gif&h=bfed7571&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d0JcVKF.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd0JcVKF.gif&h=ba39d79a&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yby8t4G.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYby8t4G.gif&h=5ff300ac&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />為表誠意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c762146cad9577b9245d3bfea80b3781b433f00","tid":2205313,"uid":150831,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T17:49:07.000Z","msg":"借問聲係咩APP嚟？@@"},{"pid":"8f749fb86235c0eaedc0042419478580d12bbae7","tid":2205313,"uid":124400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c762146cad9577b9245d3bfea80b3781b433f00","tid":2205313,"uid":150831,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T17:49:07.000Z","msg":"借問聲係咩APP嚟？@@"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T17:54:11.000Z","msg":"主要係俾人交換下D唔用嘅野"},{"pid":"39578a5b1bc27c46848dfb52628177219f092442","tid":2205313,"uid":283951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T18:14:52.000Z","msg":"留名加幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90ed0f84ba009d40df8c4fa4f4b55be3b0a5baf1","tid":2205313,"uid":72228,"like